Rating: 3
I originally was interested in this recipe, because the ingredients sounded like they would make a good sauce. I was a bit hesitant when I read some of the negative reviews on the taste of the sauce. I decided to make it anyway last night. I think that the problem with this recipe is the measurements. One whole cup of ANY KIND of vinegar would kill a sauce! I cut the amount to 1/3 cup. Also, 1/2 cup of brown sugar is PLENTY to sweeten the sauce. I was also conservative with the cayenne. With these changes, my chicken was delicious and my husband loved it! Try it my way!! You'll like it!

