Rating: 2
I don't understand why this is a four-fork recipe. The chicken was much too tangy (almost sour), and I expected the sauce to be thicker, sort of like the barbecue sauces you buy at the store. It wasn't horrible, but there are probably better recipes out there. Personally, I think slapping on some K.C. Masterpiece would have made for better barbecued chicken, but apparently that's just me!

